727370f-b.title: Queens: Maurice Avenue - 66th Street
727370f-b.text:
6550 Maurice Ave., south side, between 66th Street (left) and
65th Place (right), showing the John Bowne Hyatt house from 1852-1860.
Another owner of this house was Thomas Burroughs (grandson of Thomas
Burroughs and Sarah Wyckoff of Flatlands) from 1873 to 1896.
March 1923.
View 2: January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
